channel.title: Skater sigs\pics
channel.description:
[Center]Hey guys, I dunno if u can tell but i love skating([sup]boarding[/sup]), I have Supra vulk lows and i decided hey because their good why not make a sig about them? so i tried and it looked really good if you guys are into skating, or anything as a matter of fact i can make sigs for you, just tell me a brand name and il do it. heres the one that i just recently made! (btw im not a nerd guy who makes those crazy ass sigs, plain and simple)
[URL=http://img471.imageshack.us/my.php?image=shoesgoodpu4.jpg][IMG]http://img471.imageshack.us/img471/1073/shoesgoodpu4.th.jpg[/img][/URL]
Anyways hope u like ;D ([sub]click on image to see full pic[/sub])[/center]
